headline: Should ONEOK's (OKE) Strong Synergy Gains Offset Concerns Over a Moderated 2026 Outlook?
summary: ONEOK recently reported third-quarter results that exceeded expectations and announced achieving nearly US$500 million in acquisition synergies year-to-date, reflecting operational advances and growth in pipeline volumes and new project ramp-ups. An interesting insight is that these synergies and improved operational performance were delivered despite management moderating its 2026 outlook due to ongoing commodity price volatility. We’ll now explore how the company’s strong synergy...
